HEADWORD: Laryngoscopic
<hw>La*ryn`go*scop"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to the inspection of the larynx; of or pertaining to the
laryngoscope or laryngoscopy.</def>⟦br⟧
